API Design Process:

    1. Review API Requirements
    2. Identify the main resources and Entites
    3. Use HTTP Methods to Assign Action on Resource.


    1. Review API Requirments:

        A Requirements came to create a rest API for Customer Relationship Management System.

        So here we will allow the Rest Clients to:
        1. get the list of customers
        2. Get Single Customer by ID.
        3. Update the Customer
        4. Delete the Customer

    2. Identify the main Resources/ Entity

    3. Use HTTP Methods on the entity to perform actions:
        GET, POST, PUT, DELTE